    <item>
      <title>更多中国白领表示工资正在下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/more-of-china-s-white-collar-workers-say-their-wages-are-falling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近三分之一的中国上班族表示去年工资下降，这是至少六年来的最高比例，凸显了世界第二大经济体持续存在的通货紧缩压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/more-of-china-s-white-collar-workers-say-their-wages-are-falling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
